floor_guide: On the day of the event, an online venue will be available at reBako. Live streaming of sessions and Ask the Speaker will take place at the reBako venue. To move from one venue to another, please follow the directions in the venue and use the portals (like warp zones). If the venue is full, you will be redirected to a page called "Gate", so please move to an available venue.
